  <p>Asynchronously polls <code>drive</code> to see if media has been inserted or removed.</p>  <p>When the operation is finished, <code>callback</code> will be called.
You can then call <link xref="Gio.poll_for_media_finish"/> to obtain the
result of the operation.</p>

